{"tid":411594,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[燃系galgame推介] Baldr Heart","createTime":"2017-09-24T03:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T12:45:31.000Z","uid":5590,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"77a399dfbd9aaf6b1b6965f19efa41869664bee1","tid":411594,"uid":5590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T03:20:15.000Z","msg":"第一次接觸Baldr系列，眼見Baldr Bringer十月出而且是該系列最終章。趕緊玩一下前作Baldr Heart試試水溫。一玩結果超出預期，不愧是戯画招牌系列，決定出文吹奏。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/105533_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F105533_3fb2db6cccf4a23383383394b28b2b31.jpg&h=91cd3e83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n官網 <a href=\"http://products.web-giga.com/baldrheart/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fproducts.web-giga.com%2Fbaldrheart%2F&d=hUUeBhi%2FZbZ2J%2Bxlb%2FwNl8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=baad0ff1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://products.web-giga.com/baldrheart/</a><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n簡評：燃，感動 <br />\n<br />\n劇情非常優秀，王道硬派，節奏快不嘮叨不划水，伏筆有心思。Baldr Heart劇情和戰鬥安排恰到好處，每一章都有戰鬥，劇情緊湊跌宕，鋒迴路轉。尤其是凪線後半一路殺進去，神OP插入燃到不行。最終BOSS難度爆炸，配上BGM有濃濃dark soul味。玩家熱血戰鬥守護女主，代入感超強。單論劇本足以戰翻2016年銷量頭三名。<br />\n<br />\n限制攻略次序，月咏&gt;茉緒&gt;妹妹&gt;凪。因為限制次序，前期角色變成解迷用的踏腳石。三條角色線嚴重壓縮，刪去日常，戀愛直白，成全了凪卻犧牲了其他人。而月咏人設非常合我胃口，失憶少女+大和撫子。月咏的身世和記憶是解迷關鍵，但偏偏是第一位攻略。令到高潮部份欲言又止，而感情線更是一發直球，莫名其妙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/105907_08046f7aaf85754115b2d3dbfb8580cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F105907_08046f7aaf85754115b2d3dbfb8580cb.jpg&h=46fa65a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGE二人隱世生活，但男主一部分的心留到島上，心靈空虛，迷題沒有解決也沒有人得到救贖，比BE更BE。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/105913_ea6e7edcf144b6854b8e9691e167592b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F105913_ea6e7edcf144b6854b8e9691e167592b.jpg&h=f2920719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n茉緒線的迷題只出現在個人線，側面補充細節，在其他線存在依然薄弱。BE原因勉強但震撼虐心。<br />\n <br />\n<del> 妹線對人設無好感，略過。</del><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/110129_5266b3f4a3423ef5a6cd92925c7e7e71.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F110129_5266b3f4a3423ef5a6cd92925c7e7e71.jpg&h=7f6949e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n凪線作為收盤全劇迷題以她為核心展開，長度比其他角色多一倍，亦多得其他線壓縮，凪線有著豐富的互動，最激昂的戰鬥，各種回憶殺鋪墊身世。最想不到是凪的存在，伏筆埋得非常巧妙，線索明明擺在眼前最終才晃然大悟，正如官方寫的「見えるものを疑え。見えないものを信じろ。」，滿分扣題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/105919_2c0ca90fd9c2bda80142e2a317c81f1b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F105919_2c0ca90fd9c2bda80142e2a317c81f1b.jpg&h=d92b5b3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個人認為轉生結局最觸動心靈，男主再次離開故鄉尋找失去的記憶，在船上重遇轉生失憶的凪，萬般思緒在心頭卻想不起因由。二人一起踏上尋找記憶的旅程，殊不知大家找的人是對方。如此虐心又帶點希冀的結局，筆者推完久久不能平伏心情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/110208_c37e5ff89ccd5ced387760f9f266e80b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F110208_c37e5ff89ccd5ced387760f9f266e80b.jpg&h=26931142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n病嬌幼馴染BOSS美咲，她的誕生是悲劇，出生記憶人格是別人給予，唯獨對男主的愛是真。她真摯的愛超越所有女角，亦因為她的偏執把自己推向絕路，如果有個人線應該很精彩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/110215_8e43a9037cfeddc5f955ec1239949ccc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F110215_8e43a9037cfeddc5f955ec1239949ccc.jpg&h=b646bbfd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n配角以芺蕾雅最有血有肉，同伴背負污名死光，自己失去肉體，三十年來一直追查真相未曾休息。救場誘餌堵追兵，帶領後輩殺出重圍，來回地獄拖BOSS，各場激戰總有她的身影，賺人熱淚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sdZ5Pi21Dd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsdZ5Pi21Dd4&d=hUUeBhi%2FZbZ2J%2Bxlb%2FwNl8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=8138a004\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sdZ5Pi21Dd4</a><br />\nBaldr系列賣點當然是熱血爽快的戰鬥系統，Baldr Heart近戰連技簡直是藝術，遊戲最難的不是BOSS戰，而是排山倒海的雜卒<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">本人手殘黨只能normal過關</span>加上兵裝少女育成，減少多週目通關的枯燥。文字表達不到有幾爽快，玩一遍就明。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n總結: Baldr Heart有著優秀劇情，爽快淋漓戰鬥系統，各種虐心治癒結局，絕對值得一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffa5ecd17c2a8472cf288013a0eef2de9328c158","tid":411594,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:11:55.000Z","msg":"最緊要係...有冇中字"},{"pid":"45b081b5c2b4cc5728749e47b234217895646ec1","tid":411594,"uid":5590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:19:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要係...有冇中字</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://sukebei.nyaa.si/view/2283051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsukebei.nyaa.si%2Fview%2F2283051&d=hUUeBhi%2FZbZ2J%2Bxlb%2FwNl8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=83226b70\" target=\"_blank\">https://sukebei.nyaa.si/view/2283051</a>"},{"pid":"105bac56559fbe7c9dba1b72fad1811c90d195da","tid":411594,"uid":13151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:43:41.000Z","msg":"正,啱啱想塭隻Galgame玩吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw好少接觸燃系galgame, 對上一隻應該係rewrite (算唔算?)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094fe99079ab6f95c5da4541b42fa98ffad9a6b7","tid":411594,"uid":5590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正,啱啱想塭隻Galgame玩吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw好少接觸燃系galgame, 對上一隻應該係rewrite (算唔算?)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n玩埋呢隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/379018/page/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/379018/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"7f7bac3cfabb38f80f4073a72b3e636b707496dc","tid":411594,"uid":5590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:45:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}